name: ext_R4B_ElementDefinition_defaultValue
title: Cross-version Extension for R4B.ElementDefinition.defaultValue[x] for use in FHIR R4
description: This cross-version extension represents ElementDefinition.defaultValue[x] from http://hl7.org/fhir/StructureDefinition/ElementDefinition|4.3.0 for use in FHIR R4.

element.short: Specified value if missing from instance
element.definition: The value that should be used if there is no value stated in the instance (e.g. 'if not otherwise specified, the abstract is false').
element.comment: `ElementDefinition.defaultValue[x]` maps to R4 `ElementDefinition.defaultValue[x]`. Added the types: `Meta` So is mapped as RelatedTo.
